729522f-a.title: Richmond: Richmond Terrace - Catherine Street
729522f-a.text:
3603 and 3599 Richmond Terace, north side, between Catharine Street and Linfield Avenue. No. 3603 is an old brick-lined house. It belonged to J.Anderson (1874 and
1898 maps). No. 3599 is a Decker house.
September 25, 1931
P. L. Sperr
